	(text "PLEASE Bring your own load dump protection! \n\nTinySparrow doesn't include this as it's\ndesigned to be a core module. Keep in mind that\nthe carrier board as well as any ancillary stuff\non there would require this protection too anyway.\n(Those devices should be powered through the\ncarrier, not through TinySparrow.)"
